These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: pop, indie, punk, jazz, country, electronic, funk
1. the fan of indie is in the middle##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of punk##1
5. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
6. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Music-Genre   | funk | jazz | country | indie | punk | pop | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: turquise, lavender, blood-red, mauve, grey, blue, lilac
1. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
4. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
6. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Color   | turquise | grey | blood-red | blue | mauve | lavender | lilac |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
House: cape-cod, art-deco, colonial, tower, townhouse, gothic-revival, futuristic
1. the tower house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
2. the colonial house is in the middle##1
3. the tower house is on the far right##1
4. the futuristic house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
6. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| House   | townhouse | cape-cod | gothic-revival | colonial | futuristic | art-deco | tower |

