2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3   |  4  |    5    |   6   |  7   |
| Birthday   | february | june | september | august | march | may | december |

